"     <li>",
"      Carbocysteine Sodium",
"     </li>",
"    </ul>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"list_set htclist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\" id=\"F1978172\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Pharmacologic Category",
"    </span>",
"    <ul>",
"     <li>",
"      <span class=\"list-set-name\">",
"       Mucolytic Agent",
"      </span>",
"     </li>",
"    </ul>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block iuse drugH1Div\" id=\"F1978175\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Reported Use",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Decreases excessive mucous production; may be used in acute or chronic bronchitis, rhinopharyngitis, tracheitis, acute or subacute laryngitis, otitis, and sinusitis",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block idos drugH1Div\" id=\"F1978170\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Dosage Range",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Oral: Chronic bronchitis:",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Children 2-5 years: 62.5-125 mg 4 times/day",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Children 6-12 years: 250 mg 3 times/day",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Adults: 750 mg 3 times/day; reduce dose by",
"     <sup>",
"      1",
"     </sup>",
"     /",
"     <sub>",
"      3",
"     </sub>",
"     when a significant response is obtained",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block prod-avail drugH1Div\" id=\"F11821186\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Product Availability",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Product available in various countries; not currently available in the U.S.",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block foc drugH1Div\" id=\"F1978174\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Dosage Forms",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justified;\">",
"     Capsule: 375 mg",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justified;\">",
"     Syrup: 2 g/100 mL (125 mL); 5 g/100 mL (125 mL)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justified;\">",
"     Syrup, as sodium: 250 mg/5 mL (90 mL, 200 mL)",
"    </p>",
