"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Perfusion scanning enhances risk stratification in patients with angina",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 457px; height: 275px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    In a study of 102 patients with stable angina and a normal or nondiagnostic ECG, a Tc-99m sestamibi perfusion scan stratified patients at low, intermediate, or high risk for a cardiac event. The results of the perfusion scan were more helpful than the ECG and clinical variables; multivariate regression analysis identified an abnormal perfusion test as the only independent predictor of cardiac events.",
